{"tid":1969870,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"9 人新男團 CRAVITY 個人照到齊　敲定 4 月中出道！","createTime":"2020-04-12T17:22:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-13T02:29:06.000Z","uid":149371,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1f108452142ad5fa985752c187a9d205e8d29758","tid":1969870,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T17:22:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/125385\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.koreastardaily.com%2Ftc%2Fnews%2F125385&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj5MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=18709135\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/125385</a><br />\n<br />\n連日來公開成員概念照後，Starship 旗下最新男團 CRAVITY 已敲定出道日期，期待看見他們的誕生！<br />\n<br />\nStarship Entertainment 今天（25 日）宣布 CRAVITY 將於 4 月 14 日發行出道專輯〈CRAVITY SEASON 1 [HIDEOUT: REMEMBER WHO WE ARE]〉，同時公開了最新預告畫報。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rbOBrgN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrbOBrgN.jpg&h=0a6a4d9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nCRAVITY 是 Starship Entertainment 在 Monsta X 出道五年後才新打造的男團，由 Serim、Allen、Jungmo、Woobin、Wonjin（元真）、Minhee（敏熙）、Hyeongjin（亨俊）、Taeyoung 以及 Seongmin 共 9 人組成。<br />\n<br />\nCRAVITY 團名結合「創意」(creativity) 和「重力」(gravity) 的含義，同時也是 &ldquo;Center of Gravity&rdquo;（重力中心）的縮寫，從團名中就能看出他們的抱負。最近 CRAVITY 將繼續公開更多預告為出道暖身，有興趣的話不妨多關注他們的各種 SNS 帳號！ <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/X2DWCF4Vrpw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FX2DWCF4Vrpw&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj5MONXnVHdpXbsFGehQCOpI%3D&h=1dcad262\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/X2DWCF4Vrpw</a>"},{"pid":"7e0761e3a747baa16a65128999c341ad62f4cd92","tid":1969870,"uid":88491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-12T17:23:22.000Z","msg":"新名勁7"},{"pid":"64e6ffabd02ef82bf48c6bb471eea552c81b8c89","tid":1969870,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e0761e3a747baa16a65128999c341ad62f4cd92",